<p>0 down vote favorite</p>  <p>I am developing a site with Drupal Commerce.</p>  <p>The client needs a multiple recipient feature. He needs per-item per-recipient feature.</p>  <p>Suppose 1 customer buys 3 items, he will have 1 of 3 checkout box containing 1 item with all information to fill (like shipping info, gift message etc) in the checkout process and then goes to next 2 of 3 line item using the same process, then goes to next 3 of 3 using the same process.</p>